{"tid":1564303,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"又話唔推行動Po，又屌人地嘅行動，呢場運動係要持久同多人參與呀！","createTime":"2019-09-12T17:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T17:03:04.000Z","uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbcc5e06d3601f85995ee137cf1eeb637bb9137","tid":1564303,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"明白手足們都係緊張個運動會散，先係咁出po屌唱歌、屌塞商場、屌大家唔推行動po（屌人嘅po就嚟多過行動po）。<br />\n<br />\n每個人嘅抗爭成本都唔同，我相信手足們都識得分邊啲行動重要，而家唱歌呢啲只係平日嘅活動，喺提升全民參與度，宣揚革命精神上面，絕對唔覺得有咩壞處。<br />\n<br />\n除咗喺連登推大型重要行動po，日常抗爭嘅呢啲活動上面都可以宣傳行動，頭先就有手足喺IFC講915東角道，也可現場airdrop派任務文宣，抗爭辦法唔止得幾個，宣揚抗爭行動亦唔止一個平台，最重要係大家有可持續抗爭嘅準備同個人行動力，持續參與，影響身邊嘅人多啲出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n請重新聽返天琦呢段發言，唾棄教條主義！每人都做自己認為岩認為有用嘅行動，天天做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=879d8a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇返呢篇：<br />\n<br />\n日本社運失敗的歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488695</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"cc097f788b22eac43b9d85bae47190f224514814","tid":1564303,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}